This Strategy uses an adjustable counter of candle closes that cross New Day Opening Gaps or New Week Opening Gaps. An entry is taken on the candle close after your choice on the number of crosses. I have included an adjustable time based exit, an exact adjustable exit (number of ticks) and an optional break even with adjustable offset for commissions. No information or signals generated with this strategy is investment advice. Script was created with Gemini.
Open-source script

In true TradingView spirit, the creator of this script has made it open-source, so that traders can review and verify its functionality. Kudos to the author! While you can use it for free, remember that republishing the code is subject to our House Rules.

